Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.01,0:01:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}经线是流逝的岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.44,0:01:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}四季轮换 染上天蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.57,0:01:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}纬线是人们的生业
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.68,0:01:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}履地前行 震撼心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.32,0:01:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊欧夫的人民 不断编织着岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.32,0:01:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs40}{\blur3}YOLF (You Only Live Forever) 永恒一族
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.25,0:01:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如此度过数百年遥远悠长的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.11,0:01:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.58,0:01:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.15,0:01:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.98,0:01:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你再玩的话就做不完了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.92,0:01:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪亚也一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.29,0:02:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跳下来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.88,0:02:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.53,0:02:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.64,0:02:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.87,0:02:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不需要理那个野丫头的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.71,0:02:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}远离尘世 以织布为生的他们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被人们称为
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.23,0:02:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「离别的一族」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了 拉欣大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪亚下次一定要跳哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.83,0:03:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.30,0:03:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对待织物不能那么粗鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.36,0:03:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都湿成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.24,0:03:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸爸 采到好花了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.22,0:03:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 看来可以织出鲜艳的色彩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪亚 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再见…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}纱线…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你为什么在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为我是孤零零一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个人?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:03:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算有我在？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.56,0:04:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}长老大人 我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真是爱哭鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道我们为什么被叫做「离别的一族」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}外表几乎不会变化 并拥有漫长寿命的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对于普通人来说就像是童话中的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可就在数百年前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像这样的存在是随处可见的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像鸟一样拥有翅膀的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}黎明前歌唱的花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.43,0:04:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}载着水路移动的巨型鱼类
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这些种族全部与这个世界「离别」了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.28,0:04:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们不断编织着名为「岁月锦」的织物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要在这里 你就不是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在岁月的流逝中 渐渐模糊的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.87,0:05:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}岁月锦会帮我们记住的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那些不得不道别的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也会在岁月锦里陪你一起哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会陪我一起…哭泣?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 如果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你离开了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}与外面世界的人相遇的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}决不能爱上别人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果爱上的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就真的变成孤单一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算相遇了 也会变成孤单一人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}离别的一族所背负的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚安 玛琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.34,0:05:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要忘了今天的纺织
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:05:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}花开了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是雷纳特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是梅萨蒂王国派来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快去通知长老大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}长老大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}长老大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}长老大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}长老大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雷纳特都穿着铠甲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快保护好岁月锦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和传闻一样 真的都是些小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就是喜欢这种吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.85,0:09:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}退下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊索尔师长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个村的村长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这还是头一次有幸见到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然外表看上去是少女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.64,0:09:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而实际上却是年龄400岁以上的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:10:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们以织布为业 以岁月为梭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是日复一日地重复这样的生活而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.60,0:10:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不应该与你们有这样的交集
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.48,0:10:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这并不是由你来决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是国王的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请跟我们一同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.33,0:10:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}前往梅萨蒂的宫邸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}离拉欣大人远点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}女人 把女人抓起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}敢反抗的 直接杀了也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这只也得了红眼病
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要管它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在重要的是伊欧夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放我出去 放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪亚也一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跳下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}婴儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}泪酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是得有盐才够味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.63,0:14:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是长老那儿的玛琪亚吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本来是来采购岁月锦的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没想到却被困在了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里本是流浪者的聚集地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是被山贼袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且 这家伙还热乎着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母亲这种生物还真是伟大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算死了 还是想保护自己的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放着不管的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很快就会在天上团聚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.69,0:14:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这家伙的岁月锦就到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.04,0:14:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过是个渺小的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.67,0:14:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}连布都还算不上的残片罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过 总比他一个人孤零零地活着要好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的是孤单一人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抓得好紧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好紧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}算了吧 算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你打算带他走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.84,0:15:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这可不是玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:15:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不是玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是我的岁月锦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个孤儿遇到另一个孤儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奇怪的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太阳公公的味道
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}于离别之晨束起约定之花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.91,0:16:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs50}别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.93,0:16:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兰格 德雷尔 别给我偷懒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}过来抓我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs50}站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:16:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.42,0:17:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 一群熊孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了 奥诺拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乳房…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乳房…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找不到乳房
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.27,0:17:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.23,0:17:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个小孩想要抚养孩子明摆着是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是 你的孩子?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊欧夫光看外表也不知道年龄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.31,0:17:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:17:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兰格 德雷尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:18:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我 我是15岁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.92,0:18:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这孩子的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奇怪的女人 奇怪的婴儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那可是女孩的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这家伙是男孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.56,0:18:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那… 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.18,0:18:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉 艾瑞  艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.61,0:18:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是亲戚的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她会织布
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.52,0:19:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}店里面有台没人用的织布机 你就用那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是伊欧夫人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然还是瞒不过你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.71,0:19:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还请…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊欧夫人的布可以卖个好价钱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这么难得的摇钱树
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算求我也不会告诉别人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 你明明已经很不容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还要再去照顾一个伊欧夫的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.76,0:19:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或许吧 不过以后会发生什么谁都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管那孩子在不在都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:19:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}给 这个星期的份
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:20:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直以来都受你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们家的乳酪味道就是不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您客气了 下星期也请多多关照…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然就是不一样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.63,0:20:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下下星期也请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别看我这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个女人要抚养孩子可是很不容易的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的丈夫 被得了红眼病的雷纳特杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又不懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.47,0:20:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母亲到底是怎么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为我… 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.47,0:22:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会走路了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.38,0:22:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.44,0:22:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真棒 艾瑞尔真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.49,0:22:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你已经是个像样的妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.56,0:22:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.49,0:22:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪有这么靠不住的老妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.73,0:22:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们几个 羊圈打扫了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.80,0:22:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}糟了 是老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.12,0:22:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快走 德雷尔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.99,0:22:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老妈 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.16,0:22:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.74,0:22:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快点 屁股伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.24,0:22:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.12,0:22:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.63,0:22:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来 叫妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.24,0:22:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开玩笑的 当我没说过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.81,0:22:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.19,0:23:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔 你刚刚说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.67,0:23:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.89,0:23:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再叫一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.25,0:23:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又有一只雷纳特的红眼病发作了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.24,0:23:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们会马上将它处死 遗骸隔离后焚烧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.20,0:23:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}深埋到地下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.35,0:23:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在活着的个体还有五只
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.82,0:23:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.42,0:23:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}迄今为止 梅萨蒂之所以能够凌驾于邻国之上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.37,0:23:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是因为我们拥有远古的飞行兽雷纳特
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.95,0:23:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果雷纳特绝种的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.45,0:23:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个平衡很快就会被破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.57,0:23:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了保持梅萨蒂的统治力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.01,0:23:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还需要其它超越常理的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.41,0:23:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.22,0:23:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们已经将天选之血弄到手了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.16,0:24:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊索尔 那个小姑娘怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.28,0:24:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个要成为海泽尔王子妃子的伊欧夫小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.80,0:24:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到底是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.20,0:24:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们明明长着翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.45,0:24:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么不从这里飞走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.49,0:24:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.96,0:24:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们会渐渐死去的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.85,0:24:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被压抑的感情会灼烧你们的心窝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.24,0:24:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}使你们饱受痛苦 慢慢死去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.21,0:24:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅妃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.01,0:24:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}国王要召见您
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.74,0:24:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.57,0:24:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅妃 为什么总是来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.15,0:24:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里和岁月锦的塔很像
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.88,0:24:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.39,0:25:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}织好了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.42,0:25:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有好好写上去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.71,0:25:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.47,0:25:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「奥诺拉 早日康复」
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.81,0:25:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在我出生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.34,0:25:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会用织布代替文字来传达心意
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.95,0:25:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈出生的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.00,0:25:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我出生的地方呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.83,0:25:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔的妈妈说了 妈妈和其他人不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.21,0:25:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在艾瑞尔出生的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.83,0:25:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是用肚子来说话的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.17,0:25:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}痒痒虫要来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.74,0:25:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咯叽咯叽咯叽咯叽
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.66,0:25:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用肚子说话是放屁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.17,0:25:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs50}看招
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.14,0:25:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奥诺拉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.19,0:25:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要轻轻地给它盖上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.67,0:25:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了呢 奥诺拉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.37,0:26:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在爸爸和妈妈结婚的时候奥诺拉就在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.48,0:26:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果是人类的话已经有90岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.89,0:26:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔的母亲真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.72,0:26:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老是鬼鬼祟祟的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.12,0:26:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不奇怪 妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.17,0:26:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母亲对偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.63,0:26:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哈哈 他在说「偶」
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.52,0:26:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像婴儿一样
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.71,0:26:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.86,0:26:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奇怪的是艾瑞尔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.47,0:26:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喜欢母亲的男孩是很奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.28,0:26:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不奇怪 偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.55,0:26:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不喜欢妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.94,0:26:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我喜欢妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.51,0:26:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你给我安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.77,0:26:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我讨厌蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.58,0:26:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没事吧 蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.75,0:27:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}相当不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.41,0:27:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来 这个月的工资
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.32,0:27:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.04,0:27:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对了 可以帮我看一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.35,0:27:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有个客人拿来了岁月锦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.99,0:27:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.65,0:27:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「梅萨帝的城堡 与王子成婚」
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.91,0:27:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「美丽的」
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.46,0:27:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「蕾莉雅」
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.06,0:27:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 玛琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.76,0:27:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会和达雷尔说好的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.63,0:27:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让你也一起乘上货船
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.00,0:27:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看 是那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.29,0:27:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这或许也是个好机会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.95,0:28:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过 艾瑞尔要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.97,0:28:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}带着孩子长途旅行远比你想像的还要辛苦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.71,0:28:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}更别说你的情况复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.36,0:28:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔可以放在我家
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.61,0:28:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.58,0:28:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.84,0:28:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 不要挖的太深了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.60,0:28:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是… 要是奥诺拉活过来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.18,0:28:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.77,0:28:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是太浅了会被野狗挖出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.00,0:28:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.75,0:28:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把土盖上就见不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.09,0:29:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要来这里就能见到了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.12,0:29:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把土盖上就不能一起玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.81,0:29:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要好好夸夸它哦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.78,0:29:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能够没有痛苦 这么安详地离开
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.46,0:29:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们都会有这么一天的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.40,0:29:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奥诺拉只是生来就要比我们更早迎来这一天而已
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.07,0:29:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.13,0:29:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.35,0:29:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家都会死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.48,0:29:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.46,0:29:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.72,0:29:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.30,0:29:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪亚  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.43,0:29:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.48,0:29:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.88,0:29:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家会比我…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.61,0:30:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会比我… 更早迎来这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.00,0:30:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.78,0:30:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不是不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.51,0:30:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然我早就知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.62,0:30:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.55,0:30:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁先谁后根本不重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.70,0:30:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.22,0:30:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就连兰格也是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.12,0:30:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是艾瑞尔的妈妈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.41,0:30:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈是不会哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.85,0:30:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的妈妈就是这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.75,0:30:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想妈妈一定是不会哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.08,0:30:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不哭…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.05,0:30:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 别哭
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.18,0:30:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.34,0:30:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 我没哭
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.34,0:30:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.13,0:30:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.59,0:31:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.27,0:31:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在等我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.53,0:31:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好好去床上睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.18,0:31:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你变重了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.15,0:31:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.28,0:31:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然有太阳的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.06,0:31:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不会哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.26,0:31:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为我是艾瑞尔的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.61,0:31:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从今以后我们也一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.10,0:31:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前的事对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.04,0:31:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前的事对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.39,0:31:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔已经走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.36,0:32:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真的不去送他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.00,0:32:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想去外面
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.28,0:32:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等下 不是说了不行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.40,0:32:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.00,0:32:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 你不是答应过我
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.40,0:32:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要好好听话的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.81,0:32:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.50,0:32:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.14,0:32:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你还活着啊 玛琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.51,0:32:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也还…活着 克里姆
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.33,0:32:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅萨蒂觊觎着伊欧夫人的长生之血
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.80,0:33:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以才会袭击村落
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.22,0:33:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅的事也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.09,0:33:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈 蕾莉雅是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.15,0:33:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他叫你妈妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.37,0:33:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的 并不是我要他这么叫的…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.27,0:33:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我并没有生气 也没有要责备你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.22,0:33:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是想到长老常说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.24,0:33:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 我没忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.52,0:33:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.21,0:34:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天早上会举办庆祝王子成婚的盛装游行
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.16,0:34:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}王子的列队会从王宫出发
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.70,0:34:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了和从行宫过来的蕾莉雅会合
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.83,0:34:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会经过这座桥
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.35,0:34:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瞄准这个时机
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.30,0:34:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}袭击王子乘坐的雷纳特制造混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.65,0:34:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}趁着行宫这边的戒备松散的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.00,0:34:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夺回蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.78,0:34:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}偶也要看游行
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.53,0:34:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉 下次再看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.92,0:34:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.62,0:34:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.52,0:34:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.17,0:34:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}待在这里 妈妈就变得不像妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.37,0:34:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.93,0:34:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}痒痒虫要来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.14,0:34:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咯叽咯叽咯叽咯叽
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.94,0:35:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们已经将伊欧夫的血统纳入了皇室血脉
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.65,0:35:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雷纳特和伊欧夫
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.20,0:35:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}存于现世的远古传说
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.44,0:35:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们全都得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.84,0:35:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如今被神选中的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.28,0:35:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已经可以说没有敌手了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.84,0:35:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}与此同时 海泽尔王子与蕾莉雅妃的结合
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.84,0:36:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也将为梅萨蒂写下新的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.60,0:37:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.82,0:37:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}暗杀者？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.06,0:37:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}发生了什么事!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.04,0:37:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅 蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.13,0:37:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.61,0:38:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.44,0:38:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.11,0:38:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.28,0:38:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.13,0:38:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.24,0:38:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 走吧 大家都在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.24,0:38:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.47,0:38:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已经走不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.48,0:38:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.84,0:38:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}根本逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.88,0:38:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么 蕾莉雅你身手敏捷
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.05,0:38:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对了 就算是城堡的高墙也可以飞过去的…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.52,0:38:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我已经不能见克里姆了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.97,0:38:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.66,0:38:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.72,0:38:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅妃
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.92,0:38:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快走 玛琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.08,0:38:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 蕾莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.46,0:39:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快走
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.49,0:39:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没事的 我不是还能飞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.82,0:39:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别让她走了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.54,0:39:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅妃
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.06,0:39:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}追！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.41,0:39:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.74,0:39:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们要是敢对她出手的话
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.72,0:39:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅妃
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.08,0:39:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定可以飞
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.86,0:39:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个婴儿长大了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.04,0:39:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果还活着应该有6岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.71,0:40:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么样 外面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.73,0:40:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也是 伊欧夫人…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.14,0:40:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然只有一半啦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.42,0:40:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拉欣她
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.80,0:40:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}长老之所以把伊欧夫人离开村子作为禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.92,0:40:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是因为她知道伊欧夫人离开村子后的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.30,0:40:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管本人是否愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.97,0:40:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和其他人不一样就会被另眼相待 被利用
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.47,0:40:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最后就会被讨厌 排挤
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.33,0:40:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错 离别的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.59,0:40:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是始终与离别相伴的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.29,0:40:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愿你有个不太糟的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.55,0:41:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆 你的伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.58,0:41:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}至少把外套脱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.61,0:41:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}婴儿… 是怎么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.94,0:41:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成为母亲 又是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.76,0:41:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我到底算不算母亲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.21,0:41:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不懂的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.78,0:41:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都是米多教会我的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.60,0:41:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那孩子会帮我忙
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.49,0:41:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感觉就像是弟弟一样
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.44,0:41:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 又有点不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.48,0:41:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔要是笑的话 我也会很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.09,0:41:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.48,0:41:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我陪在艾瑞尔身边就能让他笑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.57,0:41:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想和他一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.54,0:42:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这话真是奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.19,0:42:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明他会比你先死
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.42,0:42:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明他会丢下你一人的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.44,0:42:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别弄哭她！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.27,0:42:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs50}不许弄哭妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.59,0:42:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的 艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.98,0:42:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆是…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.04,0:42:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔 别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.65,0:42:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你能保护得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.56,0:42:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你最重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.91,0:42:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们要留在梅萨蒂 救出蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.45,0:42:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}带着孩子的你会拖累我们
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.06,0:43:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.59,0:43:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪亚 再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.39,0:43:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要回家了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.69,0:43:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们不回家
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.45,0:43:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那大家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.67,0:43:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们两个要去新的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.53,0:43:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}新的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.05,0:43:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去米多和兰格哥哥都不在的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.82,0:43:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起哦 可能再也见不到他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.65,0:43:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只要有妈妈就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.13,0:43:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈也是 有艾瑞尔在就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.11,0:43:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.81,0:43:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们一定是有什么隐情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.65,0:43:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}万一出了什么问题你们又一下子跑了 我可吃不消
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.20,0:43:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.08,0:43:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.50,0:43:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.44,0:43:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你这臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.46,0:44:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈还要去别的地方看看
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.14,0:44:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在这个旅馆的房间里等我
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.28,0:44:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.22,0:44:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等着我 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.94,0:44:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.84,0:44:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们店主要是做酒吧的 所以会工作到深夜
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.31,0:44:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没问题吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.27,0:44:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}深夜吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.33,0:44:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.04,0:44:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.29,0:44:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还很小…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.03,0:44:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前辞职的女孩也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.95,0:44:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}年轻人做事真的是不思前想后
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.75,0:44:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.37,0:44:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.67,0:44:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有作为母亲的自觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.05,0:44:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.64,0:44:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里没有能交给你这种人做的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.31,0:45:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.55,0:45:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.33,0:45:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈 快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.95,0:45:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我跟你说 岁月锦…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.40,0:45:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要再给我找事了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.77,0:45:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么擅自拿出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.60,0:45:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看一下嘛 妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.43,0:45:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么不听我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.05,0:45:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么 刚才也给我添乱
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.02,0:45:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我找不到工作的话 连饭都没得吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.71,0:45:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.91,0:45:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么要让我头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.94,0:45:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.01,0:45:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}痒痒虫要来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.56,0:45:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咯叽咯叽咯叽咯叽
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.02,0:45:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我买了晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.24,0:46:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.73,0:46:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不是妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.31,0:46:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我根本没有作为母亲的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.37,0:46:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只是在模仿而已
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.98,0:46:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都是米多在帮我的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.65,0:46:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}决不能爱上别人
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.04,0:46:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果爱上的话
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.56,0:46:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就真的变成孤单一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.14,0:46:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真正的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.84,0:46:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}孤单一人…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.40,0:46:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈… 妈
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.71,0:46:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.64,0:47:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.92,0:47:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.15,0:47:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.09,0:47:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你到哪里去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.38,0:47:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.22,0:47:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.24,0:47:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.44,0:47:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.92,0:47:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你上当啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.33,0:47:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你一定以为是我脱的壳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.62,0:47:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}脱壳算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.98,0:47:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fs50}你笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.07,0:47:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.59,0:47:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.23,0:47:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.46,0:48:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要是一直这样不会长大该多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.45,0:48:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.71,0:48:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不长大的话就保护不了妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.64,0:48:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈你又哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.71,0:48:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不会再哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.53,0:48:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可是妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.28,0:48:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.96,0:48:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.85,0:48:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔也是 说好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.30,0:48:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.68,0:48:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要保护妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.93,0:49:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.65,0:49:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.50,0:49:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.04,0:49:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.60,0:49:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 上次欠我的要好好还清啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.12,0:49:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.08,0:49:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就只会吹嘘自己的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.71,0:49:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我哪有 别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.87,0:49:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个角度要通过经验去记住
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.93,0:49:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我早说让你放弃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.51,0:49:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我还以为会顺利的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.28,0:50:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.92,0:50:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪亚 三个凯尔派
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.23,0:50:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.46,0:50:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}马上来
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.46,0:50:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这边也拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.84,0:50:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.95,0:50:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小姐姐屁股真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.36,0:50:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.86,0:50:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过 你们俩长的并不像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.58,0:50:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 你们来这快一年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.83,0:50:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前住在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.68,0:50:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.88,0:50:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是 有人说你们是谎称姐弟
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.59,0:50:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实是在私奔
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.24,0:50:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.76,0:50:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.19,0:50:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.05,0:50:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又来了一批新的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.44,0:50:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到底要派多少人来才放心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.54,0:50:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}算了 现在是军阀的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.20,0:51:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多亏了梅萨蒂拼命地造大炮
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.87,0:51:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们才能吃得上饭
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.96,0:51:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过还是有点不寻常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.93,0:51:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是要准备发动战争了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.44,0:51:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个傻瓜王子有能力指挥军队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.48,0:51:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.75,0:51:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们一直都是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.72,0:51:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思 这么吵闹
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.42,0:51:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天就请从这上面选吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.19,0:51:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.76,0:51:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兰格！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.37,0:52:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然是玛琪亚啊 一点都没变
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.47,0:52:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这也是当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.99,0:52:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兰格你变了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.92,0:52:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么能长那么长
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.41,0:52:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别把我说得像小麦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.66,0:52:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.90,0:52:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.89,0:52:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是兰格啊 兰格哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.72,0:52:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是艾瑞尔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.93,0:52:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}突然拜访真的没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.54,0:52:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没事 这么乱 真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.67,0:52:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.22,0:52:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}米多和德雷尔都过的很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.40,0:52:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.40,0:52:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过景气的只有像特雷尔这样的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.94,0:52:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乡下全都衰落了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.82,0:52:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}德雷尔也离开了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.22,0:52:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.64,0:52:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}德雷尔也在找工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.78,0:52:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不然就活不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.11,0:52:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.16,0:53:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么 要和女孩子约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.64,0:53:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是 要上夜班
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.20,0:53:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}路上小心 艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.49,0:53:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会给你准备简餐的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.78,0:53:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他来这之后就开始工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.00,0:53:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的非常的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.15,0:53:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.84,0:53:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又不能去卖岁月锦
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.64,0:53:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且 因为我的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.91,0:53:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没法一直待在一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.85,0:53:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样啊 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.67,0:53:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他应该也察觉到你们没有血缘关系了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.83,0:53:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大概是在五年前
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.81,0:53:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他提出要分开睡的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.35,0:53:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就不再叫我妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.24,0:53:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而是用「喂」「过来一下」之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.62,0:54:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老是这么叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.01,0:54:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正好是这个年纪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.82,0:54:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也曾经有过
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.76,0:54:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兰格 你知道蕾莉雅怎么样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.46,0:54:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.81,0:54:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}连骨头也一起烧了 再把灰埋到地底深处
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.18,0:54:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.60,0:54:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没事的 梅德梅尔公主
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.78,0:54:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.03,0:54:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}海泽尔王子是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.09,0:54:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.58,0:54:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅德梅尔公主?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.40,0:54:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.35,0:54:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}据说伊欧夫人头发是皎月的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.43,0:54:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瞳孔中有金色的轮廓
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.47,0:54:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}体温也比正常人要低
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.08,0:55:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这些特征在梅德梅尔小姐身上都没有出现
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.94,0:55:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么会!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.09,0:55:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即没有嫡子 也不能继承长寿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.80,0:55:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那要那个怪物到底有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.61,0:55:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在生了梅德梅尔小姐之后 就怀不上孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.79,0:55:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}海泽尔王子好像也对蕾莉雅妃厌倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.90,0:55:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊啊 可怜的海泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.40,0:55:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}给我想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.79,0:55:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}起码再给他找个新的替代
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.88,0:55:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.66,0:55:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在需要找到伊欧夫人的幸存者作为新的受孕对象
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.32,0:55:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.46,0:55:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅妃
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.92,0:55:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果不戴这些花枝招展的首饰
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.64,0:55:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就连碰都不想碰我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.81,0:55:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就把我赶出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.04,0:55:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅妃她…
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.29,0:55:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.99,0:55:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雷纳特死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.21,0:55:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.43,0:56:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从生了梅德梅尔之后
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.48,0:56:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就一直被关在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.12,0:56:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就连见她一面都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.53,0:56:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我和雷纳特一定是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.54,0:56:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是只能在传说中存在的 虚无飘渺的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.48,0:56:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管是天翔一族 还是在黎明前歌唱的花
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.33,0:56:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在这个世界都是无法生存的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.60,0:56:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但起码还可以挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.11,0:56:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了留下传说而挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.17,0:56:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真敢说
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.06,0:56:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明就是你 把这个传说给毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.65,0:57:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请让我来赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.21,0:57:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.56,0:57:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就让我见见梅德梅尔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.16,0:57:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么不让我见她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.80,0:57:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她是我的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.99,0:57:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我已经连她的味道都快忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.23,0:57:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}连抱着她的时候那柔软的触感
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.96,0:57:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.82,0:57:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们到底要从我身上夺走多少东西
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.90,0:57:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们就这么想我孤零零一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.07,0:57:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果不能见梅德梅尔的话
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.62,0:57:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就把玛琪亚带来
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.25,0:57:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.05,0:57:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把伊欧夫的玛琪亚带来
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.62,0:57:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我已经不想再孤身一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.58,0:58:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你弄的真仔细啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.96,0:58:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为从来没有客人来过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.28,0:58:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直都是我们两个在住
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.02,0:58:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}过来帮下忙
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.10,0:58:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你又长高了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.21,0:58:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.61,0:58:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪亚 我有话和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.03,0:58:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}结束之后能抽点时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.63,0:58:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是还…
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.89,0:58:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会慢慢喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.34,0:58:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪亚 赶快去点单
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.23,0:58:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.73,0:59:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我以为是你的女人才没有出手的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.31,0:59:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.96,0:59:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好男人不是有很多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.28,0:59:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尽然被那种家伙抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.73,0:59:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个人不是这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.12,0:59:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.62,0:59:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感觉好沉闷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.69,0:59:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来 喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.76,0:59:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.75,0:59:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你已经不是孩子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.00,0:59:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.28,0:59:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 那这个应该也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.80,0:59:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来 这是加入大人行列的机会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.36,0:59:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是男人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.31,0:59:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鼓起气 干掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.32,0:59:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鼓起气 干掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.21,0:59:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.02,0:59:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是挺行的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.33,0:59:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就再来一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.13,0:59:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成为男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.18,0:59:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在找我？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.17,1:00:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个城市也不能待了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.58,1:00:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要不要和我一起回农场？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.01,1:00:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.84,1:00:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一定会有办法的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.32,1:00:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}羊奶也涨价了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.59,1:00:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把艾瑞尔也带上吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.58,1:00:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不想给你添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.36,1:00:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪亚
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.72,1:00:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是把米多和德雷尔也牵连了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.32,1:00:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我就…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.68,1:00:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.78,1:00:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}希望你能给我添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.96,1:00:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从小时候开始我就一直想成为你的支柱
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.93,1:00:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}希望你能考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.95,1:00:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以后的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.80,1:00:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以及…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.48,1:00:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和我之间的事
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.03,1:01:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我觉得我没法考虑
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.56,1:01:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为我只考虑过艾瑞尔的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.02,1:01:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么样才能和艾瑞尔一起生活下去
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.22,1:01:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么样才能像真正的妈妈一样
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.49,1:01:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但完全找不到答案
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.92,1:01:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在也还是找不到的样子
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.63,1:01:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为我非常笨
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.51,1:01:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以后也想一直考虑艾瑞尔的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.75,1:01:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.62,1:01:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.28,1:01:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下去的住处和工作的地方也让我帮你一起找吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.24,1:01:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要一个人承担啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.50,1:02:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.15,1:02:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.97,1:02:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}酒味好重
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.70,1:02:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.06,1:02:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么「我回来了」啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.71,1:02:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你怎么了 艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.92,1:02:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回家的吻呢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.23,1:02:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以前
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.47,1:02:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明每次都会亲我的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.96,1:02:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.69,1:02:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能起来吗
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.20,1:03:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别人觉得我们是私奔的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.80,1:03:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还被新来的男人抢走了女人什么的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.76,1:03:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.57,1:03:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快 站起来
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.55,1:03:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要睡的话 好好去床上睡
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.28,1:03:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能走吗
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.74,1:03:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要踩
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.11,1:03:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是艾瑞尔织给我的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.65,1:03:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看着就火大
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.31,1:03:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你为什么还留着这种东西
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.56,1:04:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你到底还要把我当小孩多久
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.69,1:04:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}永远都不会变的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.74,1:04:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.50,1:04:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.91,1:04:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个 艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.90,1:04:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们又得搬家了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.34,1:04:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下去你觉得去哪儿好
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.46,1:04:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要和艾瑞尔在一起的话
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.64,1:05:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去哪里都行
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.86,1:05:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我从来没有把你当成母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.78,1:05:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能帮我介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.63,1:05:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让我成为城里的士兵吗
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.28,1:05:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.37,1:05:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪亚会伤心的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.92,1:05:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她又不是我的母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.03,1:05:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你说了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.21,1:05:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这句话你对她说了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.89,1:05:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.95,1:05:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道玛琪亚是以怎样的心情
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.60,1:06:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎样的想法把你抚养长大的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.83,1:06:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要发嗲了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.49,1:06:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从和你差不多年纪的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.40,1:06:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪亚就拼了命地想做好母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.22,1:06:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而你却…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.12,1:06:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 我不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.29,1:06:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么那个人会将我看得如此重要
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.68,1:06:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.48,1:06:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直在我身边
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.07,1:06:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了我拼尽全力
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.47,1:06:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是觉得这样的人就叫做母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.63,1:06:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以 才叫她妈妈的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.54,1:06:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想保护她
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.06,1:06:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 现在的我保护不了她
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.90,1:06:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不仅如此 还会伤害她
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.35,1:06:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为我察觉到了这份感情
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.92,1:07:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}凭我是保护不了她的
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.53,1:07:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你这么一哭起来
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.21,1:07:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还是和小时候一样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.52,1:07:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.77,1:07:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用了 我自己来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.38,1:07:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也要出城的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.81,1:07:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等我送你离开之后
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.15,1:08:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当心点 艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.01,1:08:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.68,1:08:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我出发了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.31,1:08:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不会哭的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.52,1:08:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.14,1:09:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们约定好的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.77,1:09:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔 大骗子
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.89,1:09:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明说好要保护我的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.44,1:09:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大骗子
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.87,1:09:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不要
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.52,1:10:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.93,1:10:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还以为能看到真的雷纳特呢
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.97,1:10:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.55,1:10:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以前明明有很多的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.44,1:10:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在城里只有一头了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.66,1:10:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用这种纸老虎游行
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.52,1:10:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么可能鼓舞士气嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.59,1:10:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你听说了吗 巴耶拉好像把伊欧夫弄到手了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.11,1:10:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}巴耶拉？真的假的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.36,1:11:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}师长大人
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.05,1:11:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要再烧虱子了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.64,1:11:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好烦
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.03,1:11:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兰格师长阁下
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.00,1:11:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 是在搜查
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.67,1:11:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像是和蕾莉雅妃年龄相仿的少女
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.28,1:11:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还不一定就是玛琪亚
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.24,1:11:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}担心吗
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.31,1:11:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她是个坚强的人
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.13,1:11:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是被玛琪亚听见了一定会很高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.49,1:11:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她一直都在担心自己是否保护好艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.17,1:11:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算这样还是拼尽全力
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.89,1:11:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了让你认为她是个可靠的母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.53,1:11:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真是个小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.73,1:11:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我或许是个小孩
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.44,1:11:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 我也要成为父亲
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.45,1:12:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅萨蒂王国
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.20,1:12:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}区区纸老虎
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.12,1:12:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}竟然以远古之力换取权力
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.06,1:12:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这般亵渎 何等愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.52,1:12:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吾国必将倾尽全力来协助您
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.22,1:12:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪亚
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.08,1:12:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}终于准备好了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.56,1:12:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的头发变长了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.82,1:12:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一般伊欧夫只有在生了孩子后
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.46,1:12:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}头发才可以过腰
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.38,1:12:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来吧 玛琪亚
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.92,1:12:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们去接蕾莉雅吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.48,1:13:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要打仗了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.75,1:13:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过是一时的痛苦而已
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.43,1:13:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且你在这几年
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.31,1:13:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所受的苦远比战争之苦更甚吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.60,1:13:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}离开伊欧夫的村落
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.16,1:13:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}失去了所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.01,1:13:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个人像死人一般 藏在地窖里
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.84,1:13:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.82,1:13:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这下你总算理解我们的感受了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.14,1:13:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家流离失所
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.10,1:13:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}长老大人恐怕也已经不在人世了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.36,1:13:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们失去了一切 不断忍受着痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.81,1:13:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然而在这期间
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.68,1:13:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有你一直过着幸福的生活
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.28,1:13:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊欧夫的人民是要同织一块布的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.26,1:13:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我 蕾莉雅 以及玛琪亚
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.80,1:13:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三个人的过去必须是一样的才行
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.18,1:14:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恭喜你 玛琪亚
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.40,1:14:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样 只属于你的过去就消失了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.68,1:14:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们又能共同编织同一个未来了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.12,1:14:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔！
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.51,1:14:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欢迎回家 艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.64,1:14:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天终于能早点回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.08,1:14:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起 明明现在是关键期
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.49,1:14:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还老是让你等我
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.79,1:14:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大夫说还要过些日子才会生呢
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.11,1:14:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.99,1:14:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我还是有点担心
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.29,1:14:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我马上给你准备晚饭
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.17,1:15:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用了 别累着 我来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.80,1:15:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}稍微动一动才好
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.77,1:15:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来 赶紧坐下
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.61,1:15:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.97,1:15:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}终于快了呢 感觉有点不可思议
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.42,1:15:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我出来找工作 来到梅萨蒂王国
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.04,1:15:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟艾瑞尔再会
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.63,1:15:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后…
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.23,1:15:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 艾瑞尔…
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.47,1:15:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟我在一起 真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.02,1:15:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯？什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.46,1:16:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是巴耶拉王国的船吗
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.92,1:16:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不只是巴耶拉王国
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.15,1:16:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有雨果和恩多拉王国
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.64,1:16:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔 等等
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.44,1:16:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你保护好肚子里的孩子！
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.90,1:16:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太慢了 艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.35,1:16:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.31,1:16:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}根据传来的消息 巴耶拉王国军已经越过山关了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.08,1:16:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全员分成两队…
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.64,1:17:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是讽刺
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.65,1:17:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅萨蒂王国
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.94,1:17:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了炫耀自己的强大 使用了远古的力量
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.74,1:17:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然而 为了制裁滥用远古之力的梅萨蒂王国
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.14,1:17:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反而让邻国们联合了起来 导致了这样的结果
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.51,1:17:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大臣何在
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.61,1:17:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听说他已经和侍从们一起逃出城外了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.93,1:17:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道他抛弃了我吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.18,1:17:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么会这样啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.94,1:17:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已经完了 回天乏术了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.99,1:17:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}陛下 请赶快
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.18,1:17:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 梅德梅尔公主怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.28,1:17:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}忌讳的名字
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.84,1:18:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那种东西就扔在这儿陪她母亲去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.71,1:18:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪亚 快点
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.92,1:19:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.72,1:19:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞…
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.52,1:19:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.03,1:19:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}终于找到你了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.48,1:19:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克…
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.95,1:19:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.46,1:20:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.09,1:20:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你还活着吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.25,1:20:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还是说 我看到的是…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.40,1:20:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}亡灵？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.89,1:20:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我来接你了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.81,1:20:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下来
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.64,1:20:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那些让你受苦的家伙
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.16,1:20:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会让他们尝到比你更多的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.12,1:20:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后一切都将焕然一新
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.01,1:20:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.29,1:20:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想见她…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.14,1:20:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的女儿
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.62,1:20:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.81,1:20:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是你本不情愿 被迫生下的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.38,1:20:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 那也是我的…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.69,1:20:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要忘掉就行了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.44,1:20:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的岁月锦上并没有女儿的名字
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.90,1:20:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.65,1:20:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我以为克里姆…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.18,1:21:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家都死了
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.82,1:21:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我以为我失去了一切
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.99,1:21:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以一直以来都只去考虑女儿的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.80,1:21:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「想见一见她」
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.98,1:21:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「想抱一抱那孩子」
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.12,1:21:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}凭着仅有的这些想法
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.78,1:21:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总算是活了下来
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.92,1:21:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.81,1:21:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的…梅德梅尔
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.70,1:21:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了 蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.83,1:21:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一起…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.86,1:22:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在这里结束吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.94,1:22:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.52,1:22:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不能再让…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.95,1:22:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这群外人…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.11,1:22:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}继续玷污我们的…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.88,1:22:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}岁月锦了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.48,1:22:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克里姆
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.18,1:22:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅妃
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.57,1:23:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.00,1:23:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不论是蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.76,1:23:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还是玛琪亚
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.41,1:23:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.98,1:23:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么…
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.66,1:23:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们的时间会前进呢
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.07,1:24:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像那天一样
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.21,1:24:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.04,1:24:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}师长大人
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.89,1:24:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有情报说 在巴耶拉王国的船上
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.56,1:24:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有伊欧夫的少年和少女
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.77,1:24:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你见到她了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.13,1:24:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.07,1:24:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你走吧 这里就交给我们
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.62,1:24:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你去保护玛琪亚
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.19,1:24:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也要一起战斗！
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.56,1:24:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你对梅萨蒂王国这么忠心耿耿吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.25,1:25:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}根本不是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.51,1:25:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你只是为了逃避玛琪亚才…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.44,1:25:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.75,1:25:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开始确实就像你说的那样
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.07,1:25:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是现在 我有了蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.33,1:25:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有了伙伴
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.08,1:25:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有快要出生的孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.95,1:25:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个梅萨蒂王国
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.48,1:25:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我离开那个人之后
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.05,1:25:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第一次得到的容身之处
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.64,1:25:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想要保护它！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.75,1:25:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.30,1:25:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.12,1:25:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去找医生！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.35,1:25:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.13,1:25:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}偏偏在这种时候…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.38,1:25:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.46,1:26:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是艾瑞尔的…宝宝
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.36,1:26:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开火！
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.85,1:26:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开火！
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.02,1:26:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.75,1:26:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}加油 还差一点
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.68,1:26:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}马上就能见到小宝宝了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.99,1:27:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是这样 做的很好
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.60,1:27:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔 加把劲
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.72,1:27:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就差一点了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.56,1:27:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.41,1:27:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要怕！
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.07,1:27:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好害怕
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.83,1:27:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.63,1:27:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}害怕…好害怕！
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.42,1:27:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救救…
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.15,1:27:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔 没事的
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.74,1:27:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.12,1:27:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救救孩子！
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.79,1:27:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我来救你们
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.98,1:27:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会得救的
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.82,1:27:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}黎明就要来了 进攻！
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.83,1:28:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看 是小宝宝哦
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.34,1:28:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}马上就要出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.04,1:28:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔和艾瑞尔 就要成为妈妈和爸爸了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.89,1:28:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}辛苦了 蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.31,1:28:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.38,1:29:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你打算带他走吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.92,1:29:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这可不是玩具
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.90,1:29:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不是玩具
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.52,1:29:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是我的岁月锦
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.81,1:29:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.09,1:29:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.27,1:29:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔 差不多该回家了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.89,1:29:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.80,1:29:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.21,1:29:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你身体都凉透了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.19,1:29:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欢迎回家 艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.95,1:30:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欢迎回家
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.46,1:30:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.27,1:30:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是梦？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.08,1:30:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是梦哦
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.58,1:30:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是 下雪了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.56,1:30:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}并不是雪哦 是灰
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.90,1:30:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔和蒂塔的宝宝出生了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.37,1:30:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要勉强
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.12,1:30:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没关系的 她们会等你的
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.48,1:30:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她们会好好等你回去的
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.89,1:30:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔也是像那样从母亲的腹中诞生的呢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.64,1:31:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔的母亲当时紧紧地抱着你
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.28,1:31:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手指很用力地紧扣 好不容易才掰开
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.08,1:31:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一根 一根地…
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.97,1:31:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}够了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.01,1:31:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我没能够成为艾瑞尔的母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.36,1:31:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已经够了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.87,1:31:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你教会了我
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.30,1:31:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}温柔 坚强
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.55,1:31:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有奋斗
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.71,1:31:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}教会我如何去爱别人
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.97,1:31:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}思考艾瑞尔的事情就像是在思考自己的一样
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.01,1:31:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在遇到艾瑞尔的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.48,1:32:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我觉得这孩子能陪我一起哭泣
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.42,1:32:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}觉得你就是我的岁月锦
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.13,1:32:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要和艾瑞尔在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.51,1:32:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就能对各种悲伤和痛苦感到释怀
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.40,1:32:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是我却…对你
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.91,1:32:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔并不是骗子
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.72,1:32:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔遵守了诺言
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.88,1:32:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你一直都在保护我
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.28,1:32:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算彼此分离 形单影只
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.92,1:32:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}渐渐地迷失了自己
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.68,1:32:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即使如此 只要想起艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.77,1:32:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就能找回自己
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.80,1:32:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要艾瑞尔愿意叫我
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.72,1:32:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算不是母亲也可以
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.93,1:33:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无论是怎样的称呼
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.88,1:33:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那都一定是属于我的称呼
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.50,1:33:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把我的人生变得如此完整的 是你
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.15,1:33:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪亚
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.55,1:33:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兰格
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.26,1:33:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能帮我把艾瑞尔带回去吗
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.27,1:33:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}带他回蒂塔和宝宝的身边
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.47,1:33:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回他自己的家
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.56,1:33:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要走
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.93,1:34:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}求求你不要走
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.74,1:34:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.18,1:35:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们该下去了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.14,1:35:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅德梅尔公主
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.59,1:35:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}父王他们呢
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.14,1:35:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.67,1:35:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我没事的
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.40,1:35:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果从这里下去了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.08,1:35:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等着我的是和如今截然不同的未来
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.28,1:35:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 即使如此
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.34,1:35:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.80,1:35:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.30,1:35:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅妃
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.52,1:36:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就是 我的母亲？
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.42,1:36:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是伊欧夫的蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.08,1:36:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放纵不羁 活泼奔放 不让须眉
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.92,1:36:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}并且 自由自在
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.36,1:36:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅 快跳
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.69,1:36:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我能飞
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.22,1:36:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母后！
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.96,1:37:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛琪亚？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.28,1:37:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样呀 你也能飞了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.64,1:37:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}永别了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.37,1:37:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把我忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.84,1:37:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也会把你忘了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.97,1:37:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在城中的生活 和这个早晨发生的一切
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.96,1:37:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会出现在我的岁月锦上
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.16,1:37:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母后
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.67,1:37:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在漫长的人生中逐渐遗忘
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.16,1:37:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会永远忘记这一切
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.08,1:37:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这不过是记忆中的些微瑕疵
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.62,1:37:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我说
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.86,1:37:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.85,1:37:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母后是个十分美丽的人呢
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.95,1:38:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅德梅尔公主
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.17,1:38:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是雷纳特
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.01,1:38:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕾莉雅妃
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.48,1:38:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不再被需要的雷纳特
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.69,1:38:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不再被需要的伊欧夫
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.73,1:38:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古老的生物们终将消逝
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.41,1:38:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么至少最后就让她们随心所欲地过吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.42,1:38:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要哭了 蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.50,1:38:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没事的 绝对不会忘记的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.61,1:38:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.95,1:39:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又痛苦又悲伤
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.48,1:39:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是这么美丽的世界 我怎么可能忘得了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.94,1:39:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.40,1:39:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你回来了？
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.43,1:39:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.19,1:39:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我的？
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.04,1:39:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.51,1:40:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}软软的 有点不敢碰
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.76,1:40:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}必须得想个名字了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.28,1:40:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.19,1:40:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蒂塔？
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.98,1:40:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.80,1:40:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小时候
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.60,1:40:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我居然说你喜欢母亲很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.80,1:40:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明一点都不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.46,1:40:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为艾瑞尔的母亲太过美丽 太过温柔了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.15,1:40:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.06,1:40:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刚才也为了这孩子…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.46,1:40:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我爱你
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.75,1:40:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也爱你 可是我…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.99,1:41:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}却一直嫉妒着艾瑞尔的母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.27,1:41:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被母亲抚养大的我
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.96,1:41:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爱上了你
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.19,1:41:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这孩子一定也会和谁相遇吧
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.77,1:41:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让我们一起抚养他吧
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.81,1:41:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}靠我和蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.51,1:41:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}教会他如何去爱别人
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.10,1:41:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}离别的一族
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.22,1:41:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}见证了无数的离别
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.30,1:41:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}见证了无数的变迁
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.43,1:41:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}时间不曾停下脚步
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.59,1:41:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正因如此才能再次相遇
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.05,1:41:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}相遇并编织彼此的人生
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.69,1:42:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.65,1:42:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能带我去你爷爷家吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.48,1:42:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爷爷？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.81,1:42:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}莉莉
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.57,1:42:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要乱跑 你在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.15,1:42:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您是
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.12,1:42:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母亲3年前去世了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.34,1:42:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们是一对非常亲密的夫妻
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.83,1:42:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梅萨蒂陷落之后
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.91,1:42:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}靠着兰格先生的关系回到了这里
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.81,1:42:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然吃了不少苦
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.76,1:42:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但也算是幸福的人生吧
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.65,1:42:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等 等等
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.11,1:42:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们经常会提起您的事
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.46,1:42:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每当聊起您的时候的脸上都洋溢着幸福
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.82,1:43:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能赶上真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.39,1:43:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}父亲已经…
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.71,1:43:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回来了 艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.70,1:43:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好厉害啊 艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.47,1:43:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这么长的时间
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.33,1:44:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都努力地活下来了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.57,1:44:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.20,1:44:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不会哭的 因为我们约定过
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.61,1:44:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欢迎回来…
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.53,1:44:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.28,1:45:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一路顺风 艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.40,1:45:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚饭之前记得回来哦
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.35,1:45:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}给你
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.19,1:45:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.17,1:46:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.01,1:46:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.36,1:46:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你听我说 听我说
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.97,1:46:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.78,1:46:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早上好
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.68,1:46:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你上当了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.91,1:46:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以为是我脱的壳吧
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.95,1:46:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我出生的地方呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.43,1:46:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}痒痒虫要来咯
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.63,1:46:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你笑啦…
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.92,1:46:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说妈妈和其他人不一样
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.56,1:46:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈 快看快看
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.53,1:46:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快看啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.78,1:46:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈 为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:46:35.42,1:46:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}待在这里 妈妈就变得不像妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.13,1:46:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不许弄哭妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.48,1:46:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只要有妈妈就够了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.78,1:46:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会保护妈妈的
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.03,1:46:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.13,1:46:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:46:45.69,1:46:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.33,1:46:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.00,1:46:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用了 我自己会做的
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.00,1:46:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我先走了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.84,1:46:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没事的
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.89,1:46:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.11,1:46:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.91,1:46:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.88,1:46:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.92,1:46:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看着就火大
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.72,1:46:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.30,1:46:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我从没把你当成母亲
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.89,1:47:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 我不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.66,1:47:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想要保护她
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.67,1:47:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}凭我是保护不了她的
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.12,1:47:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么那个人将我看得如此重要
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.24,1:47:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你教会了我
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.37,1:47:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}求求你不要走
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.89,1:47:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.75,1:47:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔 对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.63,1:47:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.63,1:47:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.46,1:47:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不会再哭了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.33,1:47:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可是妈妈啊
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.40,1:47:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说好了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.89,1:47:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈 没能守住约定
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.88,1:47:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.07,1:47:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最喜欢妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.25,1:47:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.14,1:48:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.62,1:48:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.94,1:48:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.19,1:48:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还没有结束
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.91,1:48:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要我还活着
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.51,1:48:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾瑞尔的岁月锦就会一直持续下去
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.46,1:48:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不许笑我
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.30,1:48:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}长老要是看到你这张脸也会笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.68,1:48:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当然会笑了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.47,1:49:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当你告诉她离别不是只有痛苦的时候一定会很开心的
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.29,1:49:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快上来 出发了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.32,1:49:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了和新的离别相遇
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.88,1:49:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}长老大人
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.54,1:49:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我能爱上艾瑞尔真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.44,1:49:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爱过他 真是太好了
